    "description": "Awaken 是一款 2D 动作类 格斗游戏。故事以实验体3号一次意外的觉醒占领机甲开始展开。敌人势力一次次的围追堵截，哈迪斯集团的利用，你需要摆脱他们，利用自己可以使用各种机甲能力，在这个开放世界生存下来。<br><br> <h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >英雄组合技，无限连击</h2><br>《Awaken》同时可以出战三个英雄，每个英雄都有自己的独特的援助技能跟必杀技能，英雄间无限配合，击飞小怪，打出更高combo。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209660/extras/799e14a3aec3de0c109ccc3cc9a0cb99.poster.avif?t=1670829400\" width=512 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209660/extras/799e14a3aec3de0c109ccc3cc9a0cb99.webm?t=1670829400\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209660/extras/799e14a3aec3de0c109ccc3cc9a0cb99.mp4?t=1670829400\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209660/extras/2a413d378a4c40ba9bf0785a5805878f.poster.avif?t=1670829400\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209660/extras/2a413d378a4c40ba9bf0785a5805878f.webm?t=1670829400\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209660/extras/2a413d378a4c40ba9bf0785a5805878f.mp4?t=1670829400\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br> <h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多英雄养成</h2><br>你可以收集最高16种类的英雄出战，他们都有自己的成长路线，合理分配资源是前期必胜的关键。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209660/extras/4fcc44e8d4d40f8d931b6010429fb287.avif?t=1670829400\" width=640 height=360 /></span><br> <h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >独特的buff系统</h2><br>你的英雄还有更多扩展方向，插入不同的芯片，让你的英雄拥有火焰，腐蚀，雷电，冰霜的特殊属性，你是不是想尝试一下一个英雄拥有多数buff的效果？<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209660/extras/425b6b17445bf7e3f739bc5883402d86.avif?t=1670829400\" width=640 height=360 /></span><br><br>  <h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >丰富的世界，冒险探索，尽情发现</h2><br>在这个架空朋克的世界，帮助贫苦，打击强盗暴徒，掠夺他们的财富，合成能力更强的芯片，寻找真正的乐园。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209660/extras/9b086a5c5863e8381144eb62e72423e2.avif?t=1670829400\" width=640 height=360 /></span><br> <br><br> <h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >挑战精英，解锁自己</h2><br>你在旅途中，可能会遇到更先进装备的精英，挑战他们，获得能力的证明。越熟练英雄之间的配合越能展现自己的技术，精英们都是你练习的靶子。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209660/extras/be928611dacf9597afd431a3c6d4f586.avif?t=1670829400\" width=640 height=360 /></span><br><br> <h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >等等！还有更多</h2><br>§令人叹为观止的配乐，让您再也不想听到其他音乐了。<br><br>§一个又一个如此深刻而有意义的故事。<br><br>§各种选项，屏幕晃动，伤害数字。。。。。。我们都有！<br><br>§可绑定的操控<br><br>§全控制器支持（下个版本出）<br><br>§超过200多种物品种类<br><br>§传送到各个城市的传送台<br><br>§身临其境的剧情演出<br><br> <br><br> <br><br> <h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >玩家qq群：563968911</h2>",
